      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Messed Up Situation",
        "Client": "Swanky Salesman",
        "Description": "This is a nightmare... This\r\nJyuratodus jumped out of the\r\nsludge and attacked me and now\r\nmy stuff\u0027s all caked in mud! This\r\nis my best suit, too! I\u0027m gonna\r\ngo take a bath, can you take\r\nthat punk to the cleaners?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le d\u00E9sordre le plus total",
        "Client": "Vendeur chic",
        "Description": "C\u0027est un vrai cauchemar... Un\r\nJyuratodus s\u0027est jet\u00E9 sur moi\r\net mes affaires sont pleines\r\nde boue ! En plus c\u0027\u00E9tait mon\r\nplus beau costume ! Je vais me\r\nlaver, tu peux t\u0027occuper de ce\r\nmonstre d\u00E9go\u00FBtant ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La minaccia fangosa",
        "Client": "Venditore elegante",
        "Description": "Che incubo! C\u0027\u00E8 fango ovunque!\r\nUn Jyuratodus \u00E8 spuntato dalla\r\nmelma e mi ha attaccato. Spero\r\ndi poter rimuovere il fango dai\r\nvestiti e dalla borsa. Io vado\r\na fare un bagno, tu caccia\r\nquel furfante melmoso.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schlammige Situation",
        "Client": "Hochn\u00E4siger Verk\u00E4ufer",
        "Description": "Es ist ein Albtraum... Dieser\r\nJyuratodus sprang aus dem\r\nMatsch, griff mich an und jetzt\r\nsind alle meine Sachen sind mit\r\nSchlamm \u00FCberzogen! Ich werde\r\njetzt ein Bad nehmen \u2013 und du\r\nder Bestie den Kopf waschen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Jyuratodus.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Menudo marr\u00F3n",
        "Client": "Vendedor lechuguino",
        "Description": "Qu\u00E9 pesadilla... Un Jyuratodus\r\nsali\u00F3 del lodazal para atacarme,\r\n\u00A1y me ha dejado todo lleno de\r\nbarro! \u00A1Y este es mi mejor traje!\r\nVoy a ba\u00F1arme un momento,\r\n\u00BFpodr\u00EDas despachar a ese maldito?",
        "Target": "Caza un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0418\u0437 \u0433\u0440\u044F\u0437\u0438...",
        "Client": "\u0425\u0432\u0430\u0441\u0442\u043B\u0438\u0432\u044B\u0439 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0434\u0430\u0432\u0435\u0446",
        "Description": "\u042D\u0442\u043E \u0443\u0436\u0430\u0441\u043D\u043E... \u0412\u0441\u0435 \u043C\u043E\u0438 \u0432\u0435\u0449\u0438\r\n\u043F\u043E\u043A\u0440\u044B\u0442\u044B \u0433\u0440\u044F\u0437\u044C\u044E! \u042D\u0442\u043E\u0442 \u042E\u0440\u0430\u0442\u043E\u0434\r\n\u043D\u0430\u043F\u0430\u043B \u043D\u0430 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F, \u0432\u044B\u043F\u0440\u044B\u0433\u043D\u0443\u0432 \u0438\u0437\r\n\u043B\u0443\u0436\u0438. \u041D\u0430\u0434\u0435\u044E\u0441\u044C, \u044D\u0442\u043E \u043E\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044F\r\n\u0441 \u043C\u043E\u0435\u0439 \u043B\u044E\u0431\u0438\u043C\u043E\u0439 \u043E\u0434\u0435\u0436\u0434\u044B \u0438 \u043C\u043E\u0435\u0439\r\n\u0441\u0443\u043C\u043A\u0438! \u042F \u043F\u043E\u0439\u0434\u0443 \u0432 \u0432\u0430\u043D\u043D\u0443, \u0430 \u0442\u044B \u2014\r\n\u043D\u0430 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0443 \u043D\u0430 \u044D\u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u042E\u0440\u0430\u0442\u043E\u0434\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "To przysz\u0142o z b\u0142ota",
        "Client": "Sprzedawca elegancik",
        "Description": "To straszne... Moje towary s\u0105\r\nw b\u0142ocie! Jyuratodus wyskoczy\u0142\r\nz bajora, aby mnie zaatakowa\u0107.\r\nOby to zesz\u0142o z moich\r\nulubionych ciuch\u00F3w i torby!\r\nMusz\u0119 wzi\u0105\u0107 k\u0105piel, a ty\r\nupoluj tego brudasa!",
        "Target": "Upoluj Jyuratodusa",
        "Fail": "Nagroda r\u00F3wna 0 lub\r\nkoniec czasu"
